# kbot Audit Demo — repo auditing in action
# Run: vhs tools/video-assets/demo-audit.tape

Output tools/video-assets/demo-audit.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type `kbot audit vercel/next.js`
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 10s
